│ [WORKFLOW AUTOMATION LAYER]      │ ◄── Apps Script triggers
│  - Time-based processing         │     Cloud Functions (eventarc)
│  - Webhook receivers             │     Cloud Workflows (orchestration)
└────────────────┬─────────────────┘
