equests, and technical decisions → structured tickets and documentation.: Google Cloud Speech-to-Text: Gemini determines target system (GitHub Issues, Docs, Slack): Function calling triggers appropriate API: Auto-generated meeting notes with action items: Gemini's code execution capability enables voice-driven development workflows.6. Technical Challenges & Google-Specific Mitigations| Challenge | Google Ecosystem Mitigation | Reference |
